quran[13{c,v,t}:
18,62,"agay ja kar moose ne apne khadim se kaha"" lao hamara nashta, aaj ke safar mein to hum buri terhan thak gay hain """
18,63,"khadim ne kaha"" aap ne dekha! yeh kya howa? jab hum uss chattaan ke paas thire hue thay uss waqt mujhe machhli ka khayaal nah raha aur shetan ne mujh ko aisa ghaafil kar diya ke mein is ka zikar ( aap se karna ) bhool gaya machhli to ajeeb tareeqay se nikal kar darya mein chali gayi """
18,64,"moose ne kaha"" isi ki to hamein talaash thi"" chunancha woh dono apne naqsh qadam par phir wapas hue"
18,65,aur wahan unhon ne hamaray bundon mein se aik bande ko paaya jisay hum ne apni rehmat se nawaza tha aur apni taraf se aik khaas ilm ataa kya tha
18,66,"moose ne is se kaha"" kya mein aap ke sath reh sakta hon taakay aap mujhe bhi uss Danish ki taleem den jo aap ko sikhaigayi hai? """
18,67,"is ne jawab diya"" aap mere sath sabr nahi kar satke"
18,68,"aur jis cheez ki aap ko khabar nah ho aakhir aap is par sabr kar bhi kaisay satke hain """
18,69,"moose ne kaha"" Insha Allah aap mujhe sabir payen ge aur mein kisi maamla mein aap ki nafarmani nah karoon ga """
18,70,"is ne kaha"" acha, agar aap mere sath chaltay hain to mujh se koi baat nah poucheen jab taq ke mein khud is ka aap se zikar nah karoon """
18,71,"ab woh dono rawana hue, yahan taq ke jab woh aik kashti mein sawaar ho gay to is shakhs ne kashti mein shagaaf daal diya moose ne kaha"" aap ne is mein shagaaf daal diya taakay sab kashti walon ko duubo den? yeh to aap ne aik sakht harkat kar daali """
18,72,"is ne kaha"" mein ne tum se kaha nah tha ke tum mere sath sabr nahi kar satke? """
18,73,"moose ne kaha"" bhool chowk par mujhe nah pakriyay mere muamlay mein aap zara sakhti se kaam nah len """
18,74,"phir woh dono chalay, yahan taq ke un ko aik larka mila aur is shakhs ne usay qatal kar diya moose ne kaha"" aap ne aik be gunah ki jaan le li halaank uss ne kisi ka khoon nah kya tha? yeh kaam to aap ne bohat hi bura kya """
